WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:01.233
Are you saying that

2
00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:04.266
the mention of Qingzi Soup made His Majesty react this way?

3
00:00:04.266 --> 00:00:05.066
Yes.

4
00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:09.366
Your Highness, are you feeling unwell?

5
00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:11.800
I’m fine. Just need to rest for a moment.

6
00:00:15.133 --> 00:00:16.100
Now, Qingyu,

7
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.733
has lost her fertility because of Consort Yuan.

8
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:21.266
The Emperor and the Empress must be Qingyu.

9
00:00:21.266 --> 00:00:23.566
It can only be Qingyu’s mother.

10
00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:25.300
This matter hasn’t been fully investigated yet.

11
00:00:25.533 --> 00:00:27.000
Consort Yan is kind-hearted.

12
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:29.066
She would never do such a thing.

13
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:33.266
Perhaps Consort Rong accidentally ingested other medicines.

14
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:36.300
I have made up my mind.

15
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:40.066
Hmph, I see you are simply mad.

16
00:00:40.066 --> 00:00:41.900
If you insist on making her a concubine,

17
00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:43.966
I will sever our mother-child relationship.

18
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:45.600
Go to Mount Wutai and become an enemy.

19
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:54.800
It’s not good to raise your head.

20
00:00:55.133 --> 00:00:56.266
I’ll call the Imperial Physician.

21
00:00:56.266 --> 00:00:58.366
I’m fine now.

22
00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:01.300
Why did His Majesty go to the Imperial Garden?

23
00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:05.433
Because of the report you made last night.

24
00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:07.200
Your Majesty.

25
00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.266
Prince Duan is dead, dead.

26
00:01:11.266 --> 00:01:16.366
I heard he was scared to death by the tenth knife.

27
00:01:16.466 --> 00:01:18.100
Just ten knives.

28
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:20.900
Didn’t His Majesty say before

29
00:01:20.900 --> 00:01:23.066
to leave Prince Duan alive?

30
00:01:23.266 --> 00:01:26.466
The executioners were very careful.

31
00:01:26.533 --> 00:01:31.666
Unexpectedly, after just ten knives, Prince Duan died of fright.

32
00:01:32.066 --> 00:01:34.366
This useless person and that concubine

33
00:01:34.400 --> 00:01:35.166
In the past life,

34
00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:37.766
the Empress lost the chance to be a mother.

35
00:01:39.966 --> 00:01:42.400
Even in death, he should be tortured to a thousand cuts.
